<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Coaching</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.0.0-beta3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet"
        integrity="sha384-eOJMYsd53ii+scO/bJGFsiCZc+5NDVN2yr8+0RDqr0Ql0h+rP48ckxlpbzKgwra6" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/4.7.0/css/font-awesome.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="stylesheets/navbar.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="stylesheets/body.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/footer.css">
</head>

<body>
    <%- include('../partials/navbar') %>

        <div class="container">
            <!-- INTRODUCTION TO COACHING -->
            <h1 class="h1 text-center mb-3">Coaching Programs</h1>
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-8 offset-2">
                    <div class="card">
                        <div class="card-body">
                            <p class="home-text">
                                Prior to starting my coaching programs, every client must do an <a
                                    href="/get-started">introductory session</a>
                                which is either a webinar for group coaching or a clarity one on one call for individual
                                coaching.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- GROUP COACHING -->
            <div class="row mt-5 mb-5">
                <h4 class="h4 text-center mb-4">Group Coaching</h4>
                <!-- CHECKING IF DEVICE IS MOBILE -->
                <% if (device==='phone' ) {%>
                    <div class="col-lg-6 mb-3">
                        <img src="https://images.theconversation.com/files/361701/original/file-20201005-22-1an6y3q.jpg?ixlib=rb-1.1.0&rect=0%2C345%2C5483%2C2741&q=45&auto=format&w=1356&h=668&fit=crop"
                            alt="" class="img-fluid">
                    </div>
                    <% } %>
                        <div class="col-lg-6 home-text">
                            <!-- FIX WEBINAR LINK -->
                            <p class="mb-4">
                                Join my six week group coaching program and together we will work on getting you your
                                dream job.
                                We meet once a week for six weeks, and will grow together and work on portraying our
                                best career
                                selves. Prior to starting the six week program, you must join my thorough <a
                                    href="/get-started">webinar</a> that goes into
                                further detail on what to expect as well as gives me the opportunity to get to know you
                                better.
                                Here is how the coaching will be broken down:
                            </p>

                            <form action="/coaching/group-coaching">
                                <button class="btn btn-primary coachingBtn offer mb-3">Learn more about group
                                    coaching</button>
                            </form>
                        </div>
                        <!-- IF DEVICE ISN'T MOBILE... -->
                        <% if (device !=='phone' ) {%>
                            <div class="col-lg-6">
                                <img src="https://images.theconversation.com/files/361701/original/file-20201005-22-1an6y3q.jpg?ixlib=rb-1.1.0&rect=0%2C345%2C5483%2C2741&q=45&auto=format&w=1356&h=668&fit=crop"
                                    alt="" class="img-fluid">
                            </div>
                            <% } %>
            </div>
            <hr>

            <!-- INDIVIDUAL COACHING -->
            <div class="row mt-5 mb-5">
                <h4 class="h4 text-center mb-4">Individual Coaching</h4>
                <div class="col-lg-6 mb-3">
                    <img src="https://thumbor.forbes.com/thumbor/960x0/https%3A%2F%2Fspecials-images.forbesimg.com%2Fdam%2Fimageserve%2F1144542747%2F960x0.jpg%3Ffit%3Dscale"
                        alt="" class="img-fluid">
                </div>
                <div class="col-lg-6">
                    <p class="mb-5 home-text">
                        Not as interested in joining a group coaching? Join my 6 week intensive individual coaching
                        program! In this program, we will truly focus on solely you and together we will work
                        to obtain whatever goal you may have in mind. Some of the goals of my past clients were to write
                        a winning resume, learn how to beat the interview, and how to get "unstuck" from their job. It
                        is important to note that you must sign up for my free <a href="/get-started">clarity call</a>
                        before registering for the individual coaching program.
                    </p>
                    <form action="/coaching/individual-coaching">
                        <button class="btn btn-primary coachingBtn offer">Learn more about individual coaching</button>
                    </form>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <%- include('../partials/footer') %>
            <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.0.0-beta3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"
                integrity="sha384-JEW9xMcG8R+pH31jmWH6WWP0WintQrMb4s7ZOdauHnUtxwoG2vI5DkLtS3qm9Ekf"
                crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
            <script src="/javascripts/test.js"></script>
</body>

</html>